<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <!--[if lte IE 8]><script src="assets/js/ie/html5shiv.js"></script><![endif]-->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.12.4.js"></script>
    <!--<script src="https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/jquery-ui.js"></script>-->
    <script  src="assets/js/PuzzlePal.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/js/PuzzlePalShared.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-mousewheel/3.1.13/jquery.mousewheel.js"></script>
    <script src="spectrum.js"></script>
    <!--<link rel="stylesheet" href="//code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/themes/base/jquery-ui.css" />-->
    <link rel="stylesheet"  href="assets/css/PuzzlePal.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/Spectrum.css" />
    <style>
        .dialog{
            width:675px;
        }
        body{
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-left: 25%;
            margin-right: 25%;
            width: 700px;
            font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }
        .colorPatch{
            display:inline-block;width:20px;height:20px;border:1px solid #000000;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="containerr dialogr" >
        <div title="Create Puzzle Piece Print Templates" id="dialog">
            <form action="">
                <div class="wrapper2">
                    <div class="sidebar2">
                        <img class="rotate45" id="imgPuzzlePiece" align="left" margin-top="-80px" margin-right="25px" width="50" height="50" src="images/pp.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="content2">
                        You can use this form to print out the templates required for photographing your puzzle pieces or to replace templates you have already printed. Choose background colors that strongly contrast with the colors of your puzzle. White is a good choice for
                        most puzzle pieces, but you will likely need other colors too. Changing the patch size, margin, or paper size will create more or or fewer patches.  Choose a size so that pieces fit comfortably in its color patch.
                        <!--It's a good idea to print out a test page. Remember when you photograph each page to orient the pieces so that the pieces corners "point to" the corners of the color patch.-->
                    </div>
                    <div class="cleared2"></div>
                </div>
                <br />
                <br />
                <div class="wrapper">
                    <div class="contentx">
                        <!--START NUMBER -->
                        <label class="colorLabel">Start - End Piece :</label>
                        <br />
                        <input name="total" class="smallNumber" value="1" id="start" type="number" min="1" max="6560" /> -
                        <input name="end" class="smallNumber" id="end" value="45" type="number" min="1" max="6560" />

                        <br />
                        <label class="lblUpdateableNumber" id="lblPieceCount"></label>
                        /
                        <label class="lblUpdateableNumber" id="lblNumberOfPages">86 pages</label>
                        <br />
                        <label class="colorLabel">Patches: </label>
                        <div id="divPiecesPerPage" class="lblUpdateableNumber">0 pieces per page</div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="colorPatch" style="background-color:white;"></div>
                            <input type="range" min="0" max="100" value="76" class="slider smallNumber colorCount" id="sldColor1" />
                            <label class="lblUpdateableNumber" id="lblColor1Count"># </label>%
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="colorPatch" style="background-color:red;"></div>
                            <input type="range" style="background-color:red" min="0" max="100" value="6" class="slider smallNumber colorCount" id="sldColor2" />
                            <label class="lblUpdateableNumber" id="lblColor2Count"># </label>%
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="colorPatch" style="background-color:#00ff00;"></div>
                            <input type="range" min="0" max="100" value="6" class="slider smallNumber colorCount" id="sldColor3" />
                            <label class="lblUpdateableNumber" id="lblColor3Count"># </label>%
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="colorPatch" style="background-color:blue;"></div>
                            <input type="range" min="0" max="100" value="6" class="slider smallNumber colorCount" id="sldColor4" />
                            <label class="lblUpdateableNumber" id="lblColor4Count"># </label>%
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <!--<input type="color" id="color5" value="#000000" />-->
                            <div class="colorPatch" style="background-color:black;"></div>
                            <input type="range" min="0" max="100" value="6" class="slider smallNumber colorCount" id="sldColor5" />
                            <label class="lblUpdateableNumber" id="lblColor5Count"># </label>%
                        </div>
                        <label id="error"></label>
                        <br />
                        <label class="colorLabel">Paper Size :</label>
                        <select>
                            <option default>Letter: 8.5" x 11"</option>
                            <option>Legal: 8.5" x 14"</option>
                            <option>Ledger: 11" x 17"</option>
                            <option>A0:	841 x 1189 mm | 33.1 x 46.8 in</option>
                            <option>A1:	594 x 841 mm | 23.4 x 33.1 in</option>
                            <option>A2:	420 x 594 mm | 16.5 x 23.4 in</option>
                            <option>A3:	297 x 420 mm | 11.7 x 16.5 in</option>
                            <option>A4:	210 x 297 mm | 8.3 x 11.7 in</option>
                        </select>
                        <br />
                        <label class="colorLabel">Page Width / Height :</label>
                        <br />
                        <input name="pageWidth" class="smallNumber" value="850" id="numPageWidth" type="number" min="200" max="4000" />
                        /
                        <input name="pageHeight" class="smallNumber" value="1100" id="numPageHeight" type="number" min="200" max="4000" />
                        <br />
                        <label class="colorLabel">Patch Size / Page Margin :</label>
                        <br />
                        <input name="patchSize" class="smallNumber" value="136" id="numPatchSize" type="number" min="100" max="1000" />
                        /
                        <input name="margin" class="smallNumber" value="20" id="numMargin" type="number" min="20" max="40" />
                        <br /><br />
                        <br /><br />
                        <a id="aPrintYourTemplates" href="PuzzlePalPrint.html?rows=ROWS&cols=COLS&start=START&end=END&pages=PAGES&colorCount1=COLORCOUNT1&color1='COLOR1'&colorCount2=COLORCOUNT2&color2='COLOR2'&colorCount3=COLORCOUNT3&color3='COLOR3'&colorCount4=COLORCOUNT4&color4='COLOR4'&margin='MARGIN'"></a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sidebarx">
                        <div id="divPreview" style="background:#fefefe;height:550px;width:425px;border:1px solid #c3c3c3;">

                        </div>
                        <label class="caption">Preview</label>
                    </div>
                    <div id="cleared"></div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>